Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths during the event. Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom. As attendees exit, a post-event survey link flashes on monitors for feedback.

Additionally, a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, and an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews.
